    "time": "15 min",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Bayangkan kamu melihat grafik harga saham di layar. Garisnya naik dan turun sepanjang hari. Tapi di satu titik tertentu, kamu ingin tahu: apakah saham sedang naik cepat, melambat, atau bahkan mulai turun? Jawabannya ada pada kemiringan grafik di titik itu, yaitu ",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "derivatif",
            "props": {
              "fontWeight": 400,
              "className": "highlight"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": ". Derivatif (atau turunan) adalah cara matematis untuk mengukur ",
            "props": {
              "fontWeight": 400
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "arah dan kecepatan perubahan",
            "props": {
              "fontWeight": 400,
              "className": "highlight"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": " dari suatu nilai dalam waktu nyata.",
            "props": {
              "fontWeight": 400
            }
          }
        ],
        "props": {
          "textAlign": "justify"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "formula",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Derivatif",
                "children": [],
                "props": {
                  "fontWeight": 600
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": " dari \\(f(x)\\) terhadap \\(x\\) didefinisikan sebagai berikut",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x))=\\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h} \\]",
            "justify": "center",
            "direction": "row"
          }
        ],
        "gap": "3"
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 1",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=10 \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{blue}10}-{\\color{blue}10}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{green}0}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= 0 \n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 2",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=2x \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{blue}2(x+h)}-{\\color{blue}2x}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{orange}2x+2h}-2x}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{green}2h}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= 2\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 3",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=3x^{2} \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{blue}3(x+h)^{2}}-{\\color{blue}3x^{2}}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{orange}3x^{2}+6hx+h^{2}}-3x^{2}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{green}6hx+h^{2}}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}\\frac{{\\color{purple}h(6x+h)}}{h} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\lim\\limits_{h \\to 0}{\\color{green}(6x+h)} \\\\[10pt]\n&= 6x\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
