  {
    "name": "deriv_property",
    "url": "/course/deriv/property",
    "unit": "Aturan Dasar",
    "subunit": "Sifat Derivatif",
    "time": "15 min",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Pada bagian pertama bab ini, kita melihat definisi turunan dan menghitung beberapa turunan menggunakan definisi tersebut. Untuk fungsi yang lebih kompleks, menggunakan definisi turunan akan menjadi tugas yang hampir mustahil. Untungnya, definisi tersebut tidak perlu terlalu sering digunakan. Definisi derivatif harus digunakan pada momen tertentu, namun banyak sekali rumus dan sifat yang dapat digunakan untuk menyelesaikan derivatif, tanpa penggunaan definisi tersebut.",
        "children": [],
        "props": {
          "textAlign": "justify"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "stack",
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "0",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "text": "Kaidah Pangkat"
          },
          {
            "type": "formula",
            "gap": 1,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "math",
                "text": "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(x^{n}) = nx^{n-1} \\]",
                "justify": "center"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "stack",
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "0",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "text": "Sifat Derivatif"
          },
          {
            "type": "formula",
            "gap": "0",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list",
                "title": "Asumsikan \\(c\\) adalah konstan",
                "items": [
                  "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x) \\pm g(x)) = \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\pm \\frac{d}{dx}(g(x)) \\]",
                  "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(c f(x)) = c\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\]"
                ],
                "bullet": "1"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 1",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=7x^{100}-4x^{12}+9x-18 \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\frac{d}{dx}\\left(7x^{100}-4x^{12}+9x-18\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 7\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x^{100}\\right)-4\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x^{12}\\right)+9\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x\\right)-18\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x^{0}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 7\\left(100\\right)x^{99}-4\\left(12\\right)x^{11}+9\\left(1\\right)x^{0}-18\\left(0\\right)x^{-1} \\\\[10pt]\n&= 700x^{99}-48x^{11}+9\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Dari ",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Contoh 1",
            "children": [],
            "props": {
              "className": "highlight"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": ", dapat disimpulkan bahwa  ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "derivatif",
            "children": [],
            "props": {
              "className": "highlight"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": " dari sebuah konstan bernilai \\(0\\). Fenomena ini terjadi sesuai dengan ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Kaidah Pangkat",
            "children": [],
            "props": {
              "className": "highlight"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": " yang membuat hasil derivatif dari sebuah konstan menjadi \\(0\\), mengingat konstan merupakan koefisien dari \\(x^{0}\\) pada fungsi polinomial",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "formula",
        "gap": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(c)=0 \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 2",
        "equation": "\\[ y=8z^{3}-\\frac{1}{z^{5}}+2z-23 \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{dy}{dz} &= \\frac{d}{dz}\\left(8z^{3}-\\frac{1}{z^{5}}+2z-23\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 8\\frac{d}{dz}\\left(z^{3}\\right)-\\frac{d}{dz}\\left(z^{-5}\\right)+2\\frac{d}{dz}\\left(z\\right)-\\frac{d}{dz}\\left(23\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 8\\left(3\\right)z^{2}-\\left(-5\\right)z^{-6}+2\\left(1\\right)z^{0}-0 \\\\[10pt]\n&= 24z^{2}+5z^{-6}+2\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{dy}{dz} \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 3",
        "equation": "\\[ h(t)=\\frac{2\\sqrt{t^{5}}+t^{2}-5}{t^{2}} \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dt}(h(t)) &= \\frac{d}{dt}\\left(\\frac{2\\sqrt{t^{5}}+t^{2}-5}{t^{2}}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{d}{dt}\\left(2\\sqrt{t}+1-5t^{-2}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 2\\frac{d}{dt}\\left(t^{\\frac{1}{2}}\\right)+\\frac{d}{dt}\\left(1\\right)-5\\frac{d}{dt}\\left(t^{-2}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 2\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right)t^{-\\frac{1}{2}}+0-5\\left(-2\\right)t^{-3} \\\\[10pt]\n&= t^{-\\frac{1}{2}}+10t^{-3}\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dt}(h(t)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "name": "deriv_chain",
    "url": "/course/deriv/chain",
    "unit": "Konsep Derivatif",
    "subunit": "Aturan Dasar",
    "time": "20 min",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Di bagian ini, kita akan membahas salah satu kaidah penting yang ada di derivatif, yaitu ",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Aturan Rantai",
            "children": [],
            "props": {
              "className": "highlight"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": ". Untuk fungsi yang lebih membutuhkan komputasi tinggi, menggunakan derivatif tanpa aturan rantai akan menjadi tugas yang mustahil. Tanpa menggunakan aturan rantai, kita tidak dapat mencari turunan dengan cara komputasi yang sederhana.",
            "children": []
          }
        ],
        "props": {
          "textAlign": "justify"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 1",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=(2x+5)^{4} \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\frac{d}{dx}\\left(2x+5\\right)^{4} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{d}{dx}\\left(16x^{4}+160x^{3}+600x^{2}+1000x+625\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 16\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x^{4}\\right)+160\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x^{3}\\right)+600\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x^{2}\\right)+1000\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(x\\right)+\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(625\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 16\\left(4\\right)x^{3}+160\\left(3\\right)x^{2}+600\\left(2\\right)x+1000\\left(1\\right)x^{0}+0 \\\\[10pt]\n&= 64x^{3}+480x^{2}+1200x+1000 \\\\[10pt]\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "stack",
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "0",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "text": "Aturan Rantai"
          },
          {
            "type": "formula",
            "gap": 1,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Asumsikan ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "text": "\\(y = f(u) \\) dan \\(u=g(x)\\)",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "math",
                "text": "\\[ \\frac{dy}{dx}=\\frac{dy}{du}\\space\\frac{du}{dx} \\]",
                "justify": "center"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Recap Contoh 1",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=(2x+5)^{4} \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\frac{d}{dx}\\left((2x+5)^{4}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{d}{d(2x+5)}\\left( (2x+5)^{4} \\right) \\space \\frac{d}{dx}\\left(2x+5\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 4\\left( 2x+5 \\right)^{3} (2) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 8\\left(2x+5\\right)^{3}\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 2",
        "equation": "\\[ a(t)=\\sqrt{\\frac{1}{2}t+7} \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dt}(a(t)) &= \\frac{d}{dt}\\left(\\sqrt{\\frac{1}{2}t+7}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{d}{dt}\\left(\\left(\\frac{1}{2}t+7\\right)^{\\frac{1}{2}}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{1}{2}\\left( \\frac{1}{2}t+7 \\right)^{-\\frac{1}{2}} \\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{1}{4}\\left( \\frac{1}{2}t+7 \\right)^{-\\frac{1}{2}}\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dt}(a(t)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      },
      {
        "type": "example",
        "title": "Contoh 3",
        "equation": "\\[ f(x)=(2x^2+5x+2)^{100} \\]",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) &= \\frac{d}{dx}\\left((2x^2+5x+2)^{100}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= 100\\left( 2x^2+5x+2 \\right)^{99} (4x+5)\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ],
        "instruction": "Cari \\( \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\)",
        "accordion_text": "Pembahasan"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "name": "deriv_product",
    "url": "/course/deriv/product",
    "unit": "Aturan Dasar",
    "subunit": "Aturan Perkalian dan Pembagian",
    "time": "20 min",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Pada bagian sebelumnya kita sudah mengetahui bagaimana cara mengatasi operasi penjumlahan, pengurangan, dan perkalian skalar pada soal derivatif. Sekarang kita akan membahas secara spesifik mengenai aturan yang berlaku pada derivatif dari perkalian atau pembagian antara dua fungsi. Pada bagian ini, kita akan sering menggunakan notasi Lagrange untuk menghindari penulisan yang padat.",
        "children": [],
        "props": {
          "textAlign": "justify"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Sebagai contoh, kita memiliki ",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "\\(2\\) fungsi: \\(f(x)=2x^{4}\\) dan \\(g(x)=3x^{5}\\)",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)g(x))=\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(\\left( 2x^{4} \\right)\\left( 3x^{5} \\right)\\right)=\\frac{d}{dx}\\left( 6x^{9} \\right))=54x^{8} \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Sekarang mari kita cek apakah sifat perkalian \\(2\\) fungsi pada derivatif dapat dipisah seperti limit",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}(f(x)) \\space \\frac{d}{dx}(g(x))=\\frac{d}{dx}\\left( 2x^{4} \\right)\\frac{d}{dx}\\left( 3x^{5} \\right)=\\left( 8x^{3} \\right) \\left( 15x^{4} \\right) = 120x^{7}\\ \\]",
            "justify": "center"
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Maka dapat disimpulkan bahwa",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "math",
            "text": "\\[ \\frac{d}{dx}\\left(f(x)g(x)\\right) \\neq \\frac{d}{dx}\\left(f(x)\\right)\\frac{d}{dx}\\left(g(x)\\right)\\]",
            "justify": "center"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "stack",
        "direction": "column",
        "gap": "0",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "text": "Aturan Perkalian"
          },
          {
            "type": "formula",
            "gap": 1,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Asumsikan ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "text": "\\(u = f(x) \\) dan \\(v=g(x)\\)",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "math",
                "text": "\\[ (uv)'=u'v+uv' \\]",
                "justify": "center"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Aturan pembagian sebenarnya dapat didefinisikan sebagai perkalian pecahan. Maka sebenarnya, kita bisa mendapatkan turunan dari pembagian menggunakan aturan perkalian. Namun untuk mempercepat komputasi, matematikawan sudah membuat aturan pembagian sebagai sebuah formula yang siap dipakai.",
