            "text": "\\[ \\begin{aligned}\n\\frac{d}{dt}(W(z)) &= \\frac{d}{dt}\\left(\\frac{4z}{(4-3z)^{3}}\\right) \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{4(4-3z)^{3}-4z(3)(4-3z)^{2}(-3)}{\\left((4-3z)^{3}\\right)^{2}} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{4(4-3z)^{3}+36z(4-3z)^{2}}{\\left(4-3z\\right)^{6}} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{4(4-3z)^{2} \\left((4-3z)+9z\\right)}{\\left(4-3z\\right)^{6}} \\\\[10pt]\n&= \\frac{4 \\left(4+6z\\right)}{\\left(4-3z\\right)^{4}} \\\\[10pt]\n\\end{aligned} \\]",
